The paper deals with a smoothing algorithm for group-affine observation systems, which is a problem commonly encountered in robotics (cs.RO) and control systems (cs.SY). The problem is formulated on Lie groups, which is a topic in geometric control theory (cs.LG). The proposed algorithm involves optimization, which is a common technique in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.AI).
